Travel with confidence no matter where you're headed with the Carhartt Legacy Wheeled Gear Traveler. Built of heavy-duty 1200D Poly with Rain Defender durable water repellent and Duravax abrasion-resistant base this bag can handle any rough and tough conditions being on the road may bring.
